cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI

This paper proposes an algorithm for optimal placement of UAV-BSs for wireless communication, which involves network infrastructure and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves modeling and simulation of the UAV-BS deployment, which falls under the categories of cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The proposed algorithm also involves optimization, which can be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
